ARI 360px</strong>. </p>\n<p>Mengapa saya tambahkan <code>+5px</code>, agar stylingnya berpengaruh pada ukuran layar <code>360px</code> yang notabene <strong>KURANG DARI 365px</strong>.</p>\n<p>Semoga paham yaa :(</p>\n<h2 id=\"responsiveness-testing\"><a href=\"#responsiveness-testing\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Responsiveness Testing</h2>\n<p>Lah terus? kalau tampilan di layar gedhenya jadi gimana? hmm.. gak tau ya, seharusnya sih tetep seperti yang awal. Mau tau cara ceknya? <strong>yaa tinggal digeser</strong> :')</p>\n<p>Sini saya contohkan.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1293 497' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-31ac71bd033ec0c763f32e11cc485cf6'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-31ac71bd033ec0c763f32e11cc485cf6)' width='1293' height='497' xlink:href='data:image/gif%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAZCAYAAACB6CjhAAAACXBIWXMAAAPoAAAD6AG1e1JrAAAE5klEQVRYw%2b1YW2hcRRjeN6FoKiqIKAiV9EEEtRatTQ2BpG2U5iLYegGlCGKF6EutiigI%2bqAIItKHYqO2aWqk1SYxt62JzQ2ziU1z25hssvfs2dvZPedsds9mk%2bzl859JsskmGytpNkaSgY%2bZOef/Z%2bb/Zub7z67mwmUjfqoxo4qhehHs2Y9XTLhIqPzZiPOXjGC2F6hdQTW3W%2bbD%2bsyP%2bbg8KjxuJzweD0wmE0TRh%2bDkJMxmE8wWK2w2O1Q1BLdTwOjICIzj43BMTCCsqnA6nfTeBivZBQIB%2bEQRVurbCV5qh4KTfEwLvXc4BIRCIbjIx2w2w05j2KxW2O0TCAaD8M7Pb7fb%2bHvRR%2bsgfza2IAjQ7M65jL2Ha7DnYHUKHsuvxv6iOuSW1KPkeDNeevMajr7xO2%2b/fOIat3m8oHqF355DNXgk7wp6%2brwIKCKECScmaDGKotBCg/B4PXC7PUSIF/KkilGbHwMGAUNGF4bNInxKGH6fSDZuDhaEIstwuVycTInaLOC59x54vV4iUoUsSfy91ysS8W7eZnYy2TscDt5nJMmyMu/v4c80%2b56rxcFjjch/oWERRxuQW1qHYxT0l6cH8OnXfThXNYrKX4w4c/4vnC7Xo%2bhVLfKer0/1IxSQ7zMldegflsCKZJEQdE4iHosjkUgACSQL68eX9gnxxJIHq5TlJolVfG72PBqNQvNoQQNyirV4uqiJwOrfOPYRckqbUfp6J4qPd%2bDwK628PvJaO8dTR64mbVNQ3Iy9zzbOExCF7FPgN/gg0U6H1TAUqwzf